{
  "stem": "25209.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was quite a big Jewish population in Orlova.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I can't remember that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I remember my parents telling me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they all-- they didn't survive, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were the only family that survived out of Orlova.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know there was a synagogue, and I know we went to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But no, I couldn't even guess-- hundreds, thousands, don't-- no idea.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, apart from being told not to say that I was Jewish, I know my mother, on Friday, she lit the candles.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she put her hands in front of her face and, obviously, prayed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I-- I-- I didn't really understand what was going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- you know, I think we had a Friday Shabbas meal, I'm pretty sure.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you know we're fairly atheistic sort of a family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And during the war, my father was very angry with God.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "God didn't do it right, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I asked my mother-- I said to her-- when I grew up, I said to my mother, what were you doing when you had your, you know, hands in front of your face?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never knew what you were doing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She said, oh, I wasn't doing anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, well, why did you have it like that?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She said, because that's what my mother did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I think we lost the religion somewhere along the way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the tradition remained, at least bits of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Did you celebrate any Jewish holidays?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'm sure we did because I have a memory of apples with cloves stuck in them, and smell, and gefilte fish.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember going to-- to-- to the synagogue, and my father having all this stuff on him.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
